item.title: [718] FoHammer - Exceed your expectations!
item.dc:creator: @stultz stultz
item.description:
@stultz wrote:

[quote=“nolan2131, post:11, topic:551017”][quote author=slimdragon50 link=topic=669933.msg4480893#msg4480893 date=1429653794]

All of this is so false.

How so? Have you played the server?
[/quote]

I don’t have to play a leeched 718 to recognize that it’s not “the number one private server,” nor does it “out rank Soulsplit, Ikov,” or any other server for that matter. I promise it doesn’t have a “perfect economy,” seeing as though no economy is “perfect” including actual Runescape’s (Very far from it I might add.) Even states that “killing 5-10 revs will drop you a nice piece of Vesta for your bank;” that’s a pretty horrible “economy,” but w/e. Not to mention all of the features are, for the most part, available throughout any base 700+ revision.[/quote]

Pardon me keyboard king, but this server has charm. It takes your hand and pulls you in and its difficult to come back out. Everyone is outstandingly nice, there is a good balance of difficulty in drops, and keeps you interested regardless of your feelings towards the features offered. This is a GREAT server, and unless you plan to provide something helpful to the thread, I don’t see why you are still here. We appreciate the attention though!
-Nick
